<div class="mx-auto w-full">

<div data-controller="info-box">
  <div class="info-button">&#x24D8;</div>
  <ul class="info-box">
    <li>Use this form to add multiple heats for <%= @person.display_name %> in one operation.
    <li><strong>Partner</strong>: Select the dance partner. If the partner isn't showing, check that their studio is paired with this person's studio.
    <li><strong>Age and Level</strong>: Select the age category and dance level for this set of entries. You'll need to create separate entries for different levels or ages.
    <li><strong>Closed Category</strong>: Heats where couples dance in front of judges but not competing against other couples on the floor simultaneously.
    <li><strong>Open Category</strong>: Heats where multiple couples dance on the floor at the same time, competing directly against each other.
    <li>Enter numbers in the dance fields to specify how many heats for each dance (e.g., "1" for one heat, "3" for three heats).
    <li>On tablets: press and hold on an empty field to bring up the number keyboard.
    <li>Leave fields empty (or "0") for dances you don't want to include in this entry form.
    <li>After submitting, return to this form to add entries with different partners, levels, or age categories.
  </ul>
</div>

<h1 class="font-bold text-4xl pb-5 text-center"><%= @person.display_name %></h1>

<%= form_with(url: entries_path, class: "contents") do |form| %>

<div class="mx-auto w-full mb-8 text-center">
<div><%= form.select :partner, @avail, {},
  class: "mx-auto block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-200 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-64" %></div>
<div><%= form.select :age, @ages, {selected: @person.age_id},
  class: "mx-auto block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-200 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-64" %></div>
<div><%= form.select :level, @levels, {selected: @person.level_id},
  class: "mx-auto block shadow rounded-md border border-gray-200 outline-none px-3 py-2 mt-2 w-64" %></div>
</div>

<div class="mx-auto w-full flex flex-wrap">
  <div class="mx-auto flex flex-wrap">
    <h1 class="w-full text-center bg-yellow-400 mb-4">CLOSED CATEGORY</h1>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      <% @dances.each do |dance| %>
	<% field = "entries[Closed][#{dance}]" %>
	<div class="my-5">
	  <%= form.text_field field, class: "entry-count" %>
	  <%= form.label field, dance %>
	</div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mx-auto w-full flex flex-wrap">
  <div class="mx-auto flex flex-wrap">
    <h1 class="w-full text-center bg-yellow-400 mb-4">OPEN CATEGORY</h1>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      <% @dances.each do |dance| %>
        <% field = "entries[Open][#{dance}]" %>
        <div class="my-5">
          <%= form.text_field field, class: "entry-count" %>
          <%= form.label field, dance %>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="mx-auto w-full flex">
  <div class="mx-auto">
  <%= form.submit class: "rounded-lg py-3 px-5 bg-blue-600 text-white inline-block font-medium cursor-pointer" %>
  </div>
  <%= link_to 'Back to person', @person, class: "ml-2 rounded-lg py-3 px-5 bg-gray-100 inline-block font-medium" %>
</div>
<% end %>
